OL,5, Twitter has lost almost half of its    
OL,6, advertising revenue since it was bought
OL,7, by Elon Musk for $44bn (#33.6bn) last  
OL,8, October, its owner has revealed.       
OL,10,FHe said the company had not seen the   
OL,11,Fincrease in sales that had been        
OL,12,Fexpected in June, but added that July  
OL,13,Fwas a "bit more promising".            
OL,15,FMr Musk sacked about half of Twitter's 
OL,16,F7,500 staff when he took over in 2022  
OL,17,Fin an effort to cut costs.             
OL,19,FRival app Threads now has 150 million  
OL,20,Fusers, according to some estimates.    
